claim: Flublok (quadrivalent) was evaluated in the pivotal trial against Fluarix (quadrivalent standard-dose vaccine).
explanation: A table titled 'Adults 18–49 Years of Age, Study 1' showing case definitions and outcomes comparing Flublok (N=2344) versus saline placebo (N=2304), with columns for cases, rates, Flublok vaccine efficacy percentages, and 95% confidence intervals. does not support the claim because the pivotal trial presented in the image compares Flublok to saline placebo, not to Fluarix (quadrivalent) standard-dose vaccine.
